 .   C                     MOVELAHMHN3    K#MHN3  5
 .   C                     MOVELAHMHN4    K#MHN4  5
 .   C                     MOVELAHODRN    K#ODRN 10
 .   C                     Z-ADDAHNOBN    K#NOBN  20
